1
01:00:00,000 --> 01:00:07,250
<b>I am Tamara January, I live in Nyalabvu village.</b>

2
01:00:07,250 --> 01:00:13,208
<b>I fetch water from far away and the water table is very</b>
<b>low now. I wake up each dawn to fetch water.</b>

3
01:00:13,208 --> 01:00:18,625
<b>Our husbands have become jealous because we fetch water</b>
<b>at dawn, they say we are walking with other men.</b>

4
01:00:18,625 --> 01:00:24,125
<b>Yesterday my husband beat me for going out at dawn</b>
<b>to get water.</b>

5
01:00:24,125 --> 01:00:33,500
<b>I told him, "Let's go so you can see for yourself where we</b>
<b>fetch water." We meet men who fetch water for their nurseries</b>
<b>and vegetable gardens but he did not understand.</b>

6
01:00:33,500 --> 01:00:40,750
<b>I took him here and he agreed that there is water problem.</b>
